title: YOUBITE, LLC Recalls Pork Sausage and Turkey Sausage Products due to Mislabeling
summary: WASHINGTON, Oct. 11, 2019 YOUBITE, LLC, a Camarillo, Calif. establishment, is recalling approximately 7,197 pounds of raw and ready-to-eat, pork sausage and turkey sausage products that contain either natural sheep or natural pork casings that were not declared on the product label, the U.S. Department...
